state_summary: Fizz, a college social app, expands into grocery delivery through a partnership with Gopuff, allowing students to order essentials within Fizz's app in as fast as 15 minutes.
evidence: Fizz is available at more than 620 campuses across the United States
Students are already using Fizz to buy and sell items locally
Gopuff was founded by college students and has long had a strong presence on campuses
